{"tid":1748134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日建制保皇一贏","createTime":"2019-11-23T13:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T14:15:17.000Z","uid":173191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2cc401d3ead79ae7ea7bed9e94e277748d0c34","tid":1748134,"uid":173191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:50:52.000Z","msg":"到時藍屍啲嘴臉 <br />\n啲狗嘅氣焰只會更厲害<br />\n<br />\n真係希望大家聽日投票<br />\n我拎住白卡都去投票 <br />\n如果保皇建制贏到開巷<br />\n我哋仲點樣同死者 手足報仇？<br />\n<br />\n我真係好怕 可唔可以聽日去票站投票？<br />\n敵人真係只有一個<br />\n<br />\n同埋<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好答票站外嘅問卷調查<br />\n雖然唔知有無<br />\n但果啲絕對係對家嘅選舉機器嚟</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6c36767c2a4a90d046325c3cb9adc6e827333395","tid":1748134,"uid":243011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:54:43.000Z","msg":"我一定答投左建制派、剷除暴徒<br />\n<br />\n可能仲有件西餅比你拎添"},{"pid":"0bd8deb7fcdb7b5fb93695501eb90d22804701da","tid":1748134,"uid":173191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c36767c2a4a90d046325c3cb9adc6e827333395","tid":1748134,"uid":243011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:54:43.000Z","msg":"我一定答投左建制派、剷除暴徒<br />\n<br />\n可能仲有件西餅比你拎添"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4d22b6364d63651d7e0a33ec20eed97106399b","tid":1748134,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8yQUK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8yQUK2.png&h=727d0b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等候時及面對<span style=\"color: red;\">白警</span>時唱<strong>《Sing Hallelujah To The Lord》</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港區 6:00pm 灣仔紅隧入口集合，大量兩層巴士接過紅隧，或自行行過紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【急】請傳給撞區候選人！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n必在 11月 24日 7:30am 前，在facebook發表，證明已為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7－11pm</span></strong>活動申請不反通知書，先發表就出線有票，遲發表要退選。</span><br />\n撞區表 <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FnljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=861b9b50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、所有民主派議員、及候選人。〔民主派即是所有推動民主，包括本土及泛民〕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫幫手推一推行動post拉！連登重有邊個唔去投票！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】"}]}